About the property
Zolo Amigos is an affordable Student housing PG that comes equipped with all the conveniences of a Zolo living space with a lockin period of six months. Air conditionded fully furnished spacious rooms (includes study table, chair, wardrobe), quality furnishings, nutritious food (on subscription), unlimited highspeed WiFi, RO, Washing machine and impeccable housekeeping are just a few of the perks that come included in the overall rent. Located in Satya niketan near to ARSD College,Sri Venkatswara College, Chanakya IAS Academy, Durgabai Deshmukh South Campus, Mahatma Gandhi Marg, Gurdwara Moti Bagh, DTC bus stand and Satya Niketan Local market, MCD park at Satya Niketan.
